data.description: Welcome to this charming home in the desirable Estrella! Nestled on a corner lot, it displays a 2-car garage, gated front patio, and a low-care front yard w/trees. You'll love the open layout paired with tons of natural light, a neutral palette, and carpet & tile flooring t/out. The kitchen boasts quartz counters, staggered cabinetry, subway tile backsplash, a pantry, island w/breakfast bar, and SS appliances w/cooktop gas & double ovens. Versatile den for an office! Main bedroom has a walk-in closet and an ensuite with dual sinks & a separate tub/shower. Discover the backyard with a covered patio, storage shed, and potential to create your outdoor oasis! Enjoy the Community amenities with two lakes, golf course, fitness center, pools, spas, playgrounds, sports courts, etc. Don't miss it!
